Thirty-second Ave., at the N.W. corner of 54th Street. Note the above location is for the house of which only the rear is shown. The Cemetery is beyond the house and has a 100 foot frontage on 54th Street, and a 104 foot front on 51st Street (formerly Old Bowery Bay Road). It has a 200 foot depth between these streets. This is the private burial place for the Moore family. In it are about 20 tombstones dating from 1769 to 1824. This is a set of three views from different angles.
May 1925.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

View 1 Neg#2221
